x; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">One of the strange =
little secrets of Capitol Hill is that being stuck in the minority <i>can</=
i> be a lot more fun; there=E2=80=99s a glee and purity of purpose to be fo=
und in bomb-throwing at the speaker and raining hell on the majority. And w=
hile every member would prefer to be in power, a whole host of managerial h=
eadaches arise when you have to govern. <br/><br/>But that was <i>never</i>=
 much of a problem for Democrats under <b>Nancy Pelosi</b>, who ruled the c=
aucus with a velvet glove and an iron will for 20 years. And yet, leadershi=
p would present a new set of challenges for <b>Hakeem Jeffries</b>, the min=
ority leader who is positioned to pick up the gavel if Democrats reclaim th=
e majority in November, elevating current minority whip <b>Katherine Clark =
</b>to majority leader and conference chair <b>Pete Aguilar </b>to whip. <b=
r/><br/>So far, it=E2=80=99s
been a charmed transition for the trio, who are popular with their peers an=
d enjoyed a mostly seamless succession following the decision by the previo=
us Democratic regime=E2=80=94Pelosi, Majority Leader <b>Steny Hoyer</b>, an=
d House Whip <b>Jim Clyburn</b>=E2=80=94to cede power to the next generatio=
n, while sticking around just long enough to serve as mentors. =E2=80=9CTho=
se three are a team,=E2=80=9D Michigan Rep. <b>Debbie Dingell</b> said of J=
effries, Clark, and Aguilar. =E2=80=9CI=E2=80=99ve been around a long time.=
 I am a student of the House, and I=E2=80=99ve never seen teamwork like thi=
s.=E2=80=9D <br/><br/>Now, they=E2=80=99re hoping to make the jump to prime=
time, potentially at the exact moment that <b>Donald Trump</b> reclaims the=
 presidency. Democrats on Capitol Hill tell me they=E2=80=99re increasingly=
 confident about their chances of winning back the House, regardless of whi=
ch party wins the Senate and the White House. (And, to be sure, control of =
the House is still teetering on a knife=E2=80=99s edge=E2=80=A6) These same=
 Democratic
